  "detailed_description": "Maintenance Crew is a cooperative horror game where you must work to maintain a base to keep monsters from getting in. <br><br><strong>Goal:</strong><br>In Maintenance Crew, your goal is to survive long enough for the base to mine out a piece of gold ore. After the gold is mined it needs to be refined in the base by bringing it to the refinery. Finally, you and your team can bring the refined ore to the elevator to leave the base.<br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Maintain Systems</h2></strong><br>Systems like the heater will degrade over time, repair them to ward off monsters.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902470/extras/91d56ca335aef6bd4fe405341c7b6ea3.poster.avif?t=1719412525\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902470/extras/91d56ca335aef6bd4fe405341c7b6ea3.webm?t=1719412525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902470/extras/91d56ca335aef6bd4fe405341c7b6ea3.mp4?t=1719412525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight Monsters</h2></strong><br>When Monsters get in the base, you will need to run or fight them. Luckily the base comes with some weapons that you can find.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902470/extras/fe1177687e9eab879b7a6dae3dc8a156.poster.avif?t=1719412525\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902470/extras/fe1177687e9eab879b7a6dae3dc8a156.webm?t=1719412525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902470/extras/fe1177687e9eab879b7a6dae3dc8a156.mp4?t=1719412525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Obtain And Use Tools</h2></strong><br>Tools like flashlights, medical syringes, and screwdrivers can be found throughout the base. Use these to your advantage to help you survive.<br>You can also use the security cameras in the base to see if any monsters are around.",
  "about_the_game": "Maintenance Crew is a cooperative horror game where you must work to maintain a base to keep monsters from getting in. <br><br><strong>Goal:</strong><br>In Maintenance Crew, your goal is to survive long enough for the base to mine out a piece of gold ore. After the gold is mined it needs to be refined in the base by bringing it to the refinery. Finally, you and your team can bring the refined ore to the elevator to leave the base.<br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Maintain Systems</h2></strong><br>Systems like the heater will degrade over time, repair them to ward off monsters.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902470/extras/91d56ca335aef6bd4fe405341c7b6ea3.poster.avif?t=1719412525\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902470/extras/91d56ca335aef6bd4fe405341c7b6ea3.webm?t=1719412525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902470/extras/91d56ca335aef6bd4fe405341c7b6ea3.mp4?t=1719412525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight Monsters</h2></strong><br>When Monsters get in the base, you will need to run or fight them. Luckily the base comes with some weapons that you can find.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902470/extras/fe1177687e9eab879b7a6dae3dc8a156.poster.avif?t=1719412525\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902470/extras/fe1177687e9eab879b7a6dae3dc8a156.webm?t=1719412525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902470/extras/fe1177687e9eab879b7a6dae3dc8a156.mp4?t=1719412525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Obtain And Use Tools</h2></strong><br>Tools like flashlights, medical syringes, and screwdrivers can be found throughout the base. Use these to your advantage to help you survive.<br>You can also use the security cameras in the base to see if any monsters are around.",
